    <h1>Architecture Overview</h1>
    <p>UBH is a minimal kernel over {0,1} with XOR/AND/CONST gates and SAT/XOR solving.</p>

    <h2>Layers</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Core IR: wires + XOR/AND/CONST DAG</li>
      <li>Constraints: assertions and equations</li>
      <li>Solver: SAT + XOR linear reasoning</li>
      <li>Front-ends: FOL, CNL, temporal, probabilistic</li>
      <li>NL pipeline: lexicon, typed AST, lowering, compilation</li>
    </ol>

